**Addressed**
- The two-phase SQL in [read_search_in_tx](/tmp/fdb-0.7.0-PVQ-P2-IMPL-20260527T145612Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:2324) matches the ADR shape: bit-KNN on `embedding_bin` via `vec_quantize_binary(vec_f32(?1))`, then f32 rerank with `vec_distance_l2(v.embedding, vec_f32(?1))` at [lib.rs](/tmp/fdb-0.7.0-PVQ-P2-IMPL-20260527T145612Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:2335).
- The single deferred read transaction is preserved at [lib.rs](/tmp/fdb-0.7.0-PVQ-P2-IMPL-20260527T145612Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:2324). I see no second transaction, commit boundary, cursor mutation, or snapshot contract change.
